flowchart TD

A[Patient Arrival] --> B[Registration]

B --> C[Triage Assessment<br/>Vitals + Chief Complaint]

C --> AI1[[AI Plug-in 1<br/>ML Triage Support]]

AI1 -->|Suggested ESI + Risk Score| D{Nurse Final ESI Decision}

D -->|ESI 1-3| E[Resus / Acute Bed]

D -->|ESI 4-5| F[Fast Track / Waiting Area]

F --> AI2[[AI Plug-in 2<br/>Deterioration Monitor]]

AI2 --> G{Condition Changed?}

G -->|Yes| C

G -->|No| H[Continue Waiting]

E --> I[Physician Assessment]

H --> I

I --> AI3[[AI Plug-in 3<br/>Documentation Check]]

AI3 --> J[Investigations]

J --> K{Disposition Decision}

K -->|Admit| L[Ward Transfer]

K -->|Discharge| M[Discharge]

K -->|Transfer| N[External Transfer]

L --> AI4[[AI Plug-in 4<br/>Flow Prediction]]

M --> AI5[[AI Plug-in 5<br/>Bias Audit Reporting]]

N --> AI5

AI4 --> O[Exit]

AI5 --> O